Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.16,0:24:28.79,episode preview,,0,0,0,,Hey, Miria, I wonder what Czes-kun is so afraid of.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.79,0:24:31.19,episode preview,,0,0,0,,{\q0}The sha (person) in fushisha (immortal person) means human, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:31.19,0:24:32.99,episode preview,,0,0,0,,And what does fushi (immortal) mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.99,0:24:34.52,episode preview,,0,0,0,,It must be the fushi from fushidara (immoral).
Dialogue: 0,0:24:34.52,0:24:36.50,episode preview,,0,0,0,,So he's afraid of an immoral person!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.50,0:24:37.92,episode preview,,0,0,0,,That's no surprise!
